{"tid":1714690,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城online冷氣軍師]群射戰術與三段戰法","createTime":"2019-11-13T02:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T02:35:51.000Z","uid":26244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ccfa680ede758231206a5a8308954ca2f7d62839","tid":1714690,"uid":26244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:27:43.000Z","msg":"Volley fire(小弟譯作齊射戰術)<br />\n係一種軍事戰術 唔好以為好深 其實簡單 <br />\n而且更有效咁唔係提升裝備嘅底下<br />\n提高命中率同效率 正是所謂事半功倍<br />\n示意gif：<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.google.com/imgres?imgurl=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F5-15-2015%2F84B507.gif&amp;imgrefurl=https%3A%2F%2Fmakeagif.com%2Fgif%2Fvolley-fire-84B507&amp;docid=qKYhxGv5GNj7QM&amp;tbnid=I2up-viDBSZ2NM%3A&amp;vet=10ahUKEwjnquOTjOblAhXTIqYKHY3oB-YQMwhMKAMwAw..i&amp;w=320&amp;h=135&amp;bih=371&amp;biw=547&amp;q=volley%20fire%20gif&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjnquOTjOblAhXTIqYKHY3oB-YQMwhMKAMwAw&amp;iact=mrc&amp;uact=8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fimgres%3Fimgurl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fi.makeagif.com%252Fmedia%252F5-15-2015%252F84B507.gif%26imgrefurl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fmakeagif.com%252Fgif%252Fvolley-fire-84B507%26docid%3DqKYhxGv5GNj7QM%26tbnid%3DI2up-viDBSZ2NM%253A%26vet%3D10ahUKEwjnquOTjOblAhXTIqYKHY3oB-YQMwhMKAMwAw..i%26w%3D320%26h%3D135%26bih%3D371%26biw%3D547%26q%3Dvolley%2520fire%2520gif%26ved%3D0ahUKEwjnquOTjOblAhXTIqYKHY3oB-YQMwhMKAMwAw%26iact%3Dmrc%26uact%3D8&h=33b3d45c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所需嘅野好簡單 就係一個發施號令嘅人 同埋一班聽命令嘅人<br />\n發施號令者 應處於高位 有良好視野 識得判斷開火時機嘅人會較為合適<br />\n要留意敵人各種阻礙視線嘅策略 而所處高位亦應做足防護措施 <br />\n其中細節落場者應自行判斷<br />\n<br />\n三段戰法<br />\n示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dd/Ming_musketeers.jpg/220px-Ming_musketeers.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fd%2Fdd%2FMing_musketeers.jpg%2F220px-Ming_musketeers.jpg&h=231d14ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為左彌補初期火槍填裝緩慢嘅弱點<br />\n有人發明呢個戰術<br />\n大約就係第一排會根據指示先開火<br />\n然後第二排再開 同時 第一排開始準備好下一發<br />\n之後第三排亦緊隨其後開火 同時 第二排做準備<br />\n務求令到進攻好似無間斷咁<br />\n發號施令者 可以配合簡單口號如 「一、二、三」<br />\n去示意不同排嘅人士開火"},{"pid":"f85ec2fbda4d422395cf38772e93948608cd103a","tid":1714690,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:28:36.000Z","msg":"超級老豆打仔 反擊日<br />\n<br />\n防守：泊大巴 封印敵方狗竇狗宿 同時守護我方<br />\n進攻：反擊 陸路遊擊突襲對方據點 狗宿狗竇<br />\n中路：見狗車即出大技<br />\n<br />\n如果跟到呢幾步做 就好大機會贏返少少<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713666</a><br />\n<br />\n中大今日已經頂到就死 聽日只有全民反擊 否則永不翻生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712611</a>"},{"pid":"97ab87b98f1485335aeb4a6a9ae9d4cbf7037ccf","tid":1714690,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:28:50.000Z","msg":"11.14 曙光行動 繼續三罷<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/evpMOT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/evpMOT</a><br />\n<br />\n再接再厲"},{"pid":"02529b263ac98094618aa0624ce11cf78b660c62","tid":1714690,"uid":26244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:29:00.000Z","msg":"補volley fire gif：<br />\n<img src=\"https://makeagif.com/i/84B507\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmakeagif.com%2Fi%2F84B507&h=f52bccea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cb0e9913faebe053218f715cb025d91ef0a12d4","tid":1714690,"uid":284571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:31:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"065d0c3d9dd4ff6e7c85c8c539bde07cfaa72d69","tid":1714690,"uid":26244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:32:23.000Z","msg":"Volley fire：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTTgdj8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTTgdj8.gif&h=7e86cf36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三段：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DA02Tkn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDA02Tkn.